channel.title: LFTC: Attack of the Noobinator
channel.description:
Saw that there was a thread here that contained a few of the Leak-Free comics back in the days so I thought I'd post my comics.
This was my first comic made back in 2005 during the Leak-Free days - probably pretty lame by todays standard but I had fun doing it and hope you'll enjoy it.
